Patch Set 4: Code-Review+2

A lot of good work here, thanks to everyone involved.

There may be an argument for re-naming validate_location to 'validate_source' and moving it into _validate_source in glance/api/v1/images.py. This would mean that that function would handle all source (location) checks, both the cross-store ones and the store specific ones.

Also, there's no v2 support.

However, I think it would be unfair to block this on either of those at this point.

Thanks again!
